{"tid":1583692,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[以正視聽]運動開始走下坡","createTime":"2019-09-20T17:28:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T01:43:42.000Z","uid":303858,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c27c7186c494c08b5a2acff2f96738691983d08c","tid":1583692,"uid":303858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T17:28:58.000Z","msg":"3個半月，連登一直係呢場運動嘅主要資訊平台<br />\n但係呢幾日上連登熱門，發現開始多咗大量<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>感情po, iPhone po, 仲有大量膠po (e.g. 鳩硬冇親戚)</strong></span></span> 極度重要嘅行動、文宣、時事po就推唔郁，上極都上唔到熱門頭幾個<br />\n<br />\n我唔敢肯定話係政府、黑警滲透入連登，嘗試洗走重要po, 令我地對呢場運動冷淡，但不論係咪都好，如果呢個情況繼續落去，就代表緊<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地漸漸忘記初衷、逐漸淡忘運動，返返去雨革末期嘅時候</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n醒下啦好嘛？呢場運動一輸咗，你有部最新嘅iPhone, 有條好靚大波嘅女，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">又如何？</span></strong></span> 輸咗嘅就係民主、自由、人權。值得咩？<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以唔好再推啲唔重要嘅膠po?"},{"pid":"0acd84fe8155e056cc525e6e706d12d47b2bd6b3","tid":1583692,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T17:31:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"2932898bbacfbbae2847456b99ec27b7676f9ceb","tid":1583692,"uid":295438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T17:36:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1583462/page/14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1583462/page/14</a>"},{"pid":"3a0bf5c4b626f4bd22a8bb12df45ce860706b417","tid":1583692,"uid":295438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T17:37:27.000Z","msg":"百日抗爭宣言正式出爐！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1583462/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_bla